text: Presquille is an unincorporated community and census-designated place in Terrebonne Parish, Louisiana, United States. Its population was 1,807 as of the 2010 census. Louisiana Highway 24 passes through the community. ==Geography== According to the U.S. Census Bureau, the community has an area of , all land. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Terrebonne Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana Category:Census-designated places in Terrebonne Parish, Louisiana Category:Census-designated places in Louisiana
